    {
      "id": "context-compat-preflight",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Preflight Validator",
      "position": {
        "x": 380,
        "y": 120
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Preflight Validator\n\nBefore expansion, Twilite can inspect:\n- manifest presence/count\n- dictionary presence\n- scripts/plugins/runtime nodes\n- declared entry surfaces\n- node/edge counts\n- handle/port validity\n- requested capabilities\n\nThis supports a real compatibility decision before attach.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
