    {
      "id": "context-compat-status",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Compatibility Status Model",
      "position": {
        "x": 820,
        "y": 120
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Compatibility Status Model\n\nPreflight should classify a target as:\n- `compatible`\n- `compatible-with-downgrades`\n- `incompatible`\n\nAnd return a structured report describing entry fallback, authority handling, execution blocking, dictionary scope, and issues.",
