    {
      "id": "context-compat-block-warn",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Block vs Warn Policy",
      "position": {
        "x": 180,
        "y": 480
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Block vs Warn Policy\n\nTwilite should:\n- block clearly incompatible expand links\n- warn when downgrade is required\n- explain what will be stripped, scoped, or disabled\n\nThe user chooses the source; Twilite limits what that source can do.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
