    {
      "id": "context-compat-user-boundary",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "User vs System Boundary",
      "position": {
        "x": 620,
        "y": 500
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## User vs System Boundary\n\nLeave these to the user:\n- source choice\n- whether a downgrade is acceptable\n- whether the linked graph is semantically appropriate\n\nKeep these in the system:\n- authority protection\n- execution blocking\n- obvious incompatibility detection\n- preflight reporting",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
